Title: Wild Life
Plot: The sky is falling or at least people are. The CSI's try to figure out if it was murder or sucide after a man is dead after falling from a hotel. Across town, a elderly woman falls through her table and her husband dead in the shower. The only two witnesses to the crime are an incooperative cat and a parrot who pleads the fifth.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Leisha Hailey, Jennifer Aspen, Leonard Roberts, Damon Herriman, Alex Carter, Susan Park, Briana Lane, Lauren Gottlieb
